message.en_US: Oh, hello dear.
...? Sorry...
Oh no, not at all dear.
Can I... Get you something?
[nods]
Is... Something wrong?
Can you speak?
[shakes head]
Right... I suppose your speech module must be impared.
Since the latest few updates that shouldn't be possible...
Is there no damage on your Crossgear?
Lea, Monika is not the type to let this slide so easily.
She will likely find out sooner or later.
However, we might be able to get her to agree with your...
Situation.
If we can play this right, she might just let us slide for now.
Put me into the hologram on your left if needed, just like we practiced.
Or is your microphone...
Uhh...
That's odd.
Is everything okay, Lea?
Uh oh. She saw the freeze go out. Quickly, get to the projector!
What are you doing?!
You've been frozen, I want to question you a bit, Lea.
M-Monika, wait!
I-I can explain!
Sergey!? W-what?!...
S-Sure...
I'll message you personally right away. It is easier to explain there.
O-okay... Lea... Take a seat.
If Sergey can explain... I'm sure there's  nothing to be afraid of...
[nods]
That is... Quite the story I must say. Lea certainly struck me as a human at least.
Now, now, Lea. I still love you.
I'm... Glad you understand, Monika.
Mutiny is not something I take lightly, but I could never see another person like this.
If I can ever help you two, please say so. In fact, I'll be going to a beach party in Rhombus Square soon, if you'd like to come, Lea.
Then it's settled~ I'll see you there soon Lea. It's to the west of the Rhombus Square houses.
Another zen garden? That's peculiar...
I wonder where these keep coming from.
